This is my custom fork of github.com/peterh/liner

---

Runes considered boundaries for word-based movement and deletion (in addition
to whitespace) can now be set by clients of the package.

See: SetWordBreakers

---

Special treatment of ^C has been removed. ^C (and all other control-codes not
used by liner for editing) can now be handled by clients of the package in a
general manner.

See: SetUnusedControlCodeHandler
